      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773912791629,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DATABASE - UserDB\n\n  Table: UserProfiles\n    Id            INT           PK IDENTITY\n    AuthUserId    INT           UNIQUE NOT NULL   (links to AuthDB.Users.Id)\n    FullName      NVARCHAR(150) NOT NULL\n    DateOfBirth   DATE          NOT NULL\n    Address       NVARCHAR(300) NOT NULL\n    City          NVARCHAR(100) NOT NULL\n    State         NVARCHAR(100) NOT NULL\n    PinCode       NVARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL\n    CreatedAt     DATETIME      NOT NULL  DEFAULT GETDATE()\n\n  Table: KycSubmissions\n    Id               INT           PK IDENTITY\n    AuthUserId       INT           UNIQUE NOT NULL  (links to AuthDB.Users.Id)\n    DocumentType     NVARCHAR(50)  NOT NULL  (Aadhaar / PAN / Passport)\n    DocumentNumber   NVARCHAR(50)  NOT NULL\n    Status           NVARCHAR(20)  NOT NULL  DEFAULT 'Pending'\n    RejectionReason  NVARCHAR(300) NULL\n    SubmittedAt      DATETIME      NOT NULL  DEFAULT GETDATE()\n    ReviewedAt       DATETIME      NULL",
      "fontSize": 10.792726828835221,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "DATABASE - UserDB\n\n  Table: UserProfiles\n    Id            INT           PK IDENTITY\n    AuthUserId    INT           UNIQUE NOT NULL   (links to AuthDB.Users.Id)\n    FullName      NVARCHAR(150) NOT NULL\n    DateOfBirth   DATE          NOT NULL\n    Address       NVARCHAR(300) NOT NULL\n    City          NVARCHAR(100) NOT NULL\n    State         NVARCHAR(100) NOT NULL\n    PinCode       NVARCHAR(10)  NOT NULL\n    CreatedAt     DATETIME      NOT NULL  DEFAULT GETDATE()\n\n  Table: KycSubmissions\n    Id               INT           PK IDENTITY\n    AuthUserId       INT           UNIQUE NOT NULL  (links to AuthDB.Users.Id)\n    DocumentType     NVARCHAR(50)  NOT NULL  (Aadhaar / PAN / Passport)\n    DocumentNumber   NVARCHAR(50)  NOT NULL\n    Status           NVARCHAR(20)  NOT NULL  DEFAULT 'Pending'\n    RejectionReason  NVARCHAR(300) NULL\n    SubmittedAt      DATETIME      NOT NULL  DEFAULT GETDATE()\n    ReviewedAt       DATETIME      NULL",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
